            }

  div(class="row row--heading")
    div(class="col")
      h4(id="states", class="heading sm up") States, rollovers, and color grades
      p.
        Rollover states should be achieved by using SCSS's built in 
        #[span(class="inline-code") darken()] and #[span(class="inline-code") lighten()] functions.
